    <td bordercolor="#CCCCCC" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="70%"> <p><img src="faq_files/stamp.gif" align="left" height="166" hspace="12" width="109"><a name="stamp"></a>eLearning 
        is <b>forever</b>. Continuous education. The forty-year degree. Daily 
